  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Doraemon 2: Nobita to Hikari no Shinden (Doraemon 2: Nobita and the Temple of Light) is an action game for the Nintendo 64. It was released only in Japan in 1998 . The game is based on the Japanese manga Doraemon and is the second in the Nintendo 64 series, it was preceded by Doraemon: Nobita to Mittsu no Seirei Ishi and followed by Doraemon 3: Nobi Dai no Machi SOS!, all only released in Japan.",
